description:
Olivia Munn is back in full force - literally! In this action-packed segment, she whips out a 900,000-volt stun gun...and Sim nearly shoots himself! Olivia and Anna also delve into the complexities of female friendship, and discuss Olivia's first kiss - a makeout session that lasted the entirety of Forrest Gump! Olivia even inspired a new game: Match the Hollywood Celeb to Her NFL Paramour. (We won't say who wins!) Finally, the crew gives unqualified advice to a busy 23 year-old EMT whose married friends make her feel bad about being single. 

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
